subSubSection.paragraph:
Hosts and distribution . This species was recorded from
Agama montana
from Mozambique [ Sofala province , Beira] ( Peters 1849 ; Hirst 1926 ) and Tanzania [Liwale; Usambara Mountains] ( Lawrence 1951 ; Jack 1962b );
Agama kirkii
from Zimbabwe [Chishawash; Mazoe], Malawi , and Mazambique [Lake Shirwa] ( Lawrence 1936 ; Jack 1962b );
Agama armata armata
from Mozambique [Great African Rift Valley, Mount Gorongoza] (Lawrence 1959) and Angola [ Benguela and Caconda] (Jack 1962);
Agama mossambica
from Tanzania [Tendaguru and Kilwa] and Mozambique [Lake Shirwa and Malawi ] ( Jack 1962b );
Agama agama
from Tanzania and Congo , and
Agama sankaranica
from West Africa ( Jack 1962b ).
